thread.title: Zhenni

author: Zhenni
title: Zhenni
text: I am an International student and this is the first time I book a resell ticket online. Even it's the first time I can see Justin Bieber closely! His ticket was sold out 4 months ago. It's hard to have another chance to go to his concert in Asia. When I browse the internet,I immediately found out Ticketmaster. There were still 20-30 diffirent tickets available. I compared different seats and prices and found a good-buy which is just nearly double the original price. I thought it was ok, as I can already see him( the real person, not on screen).
